summary: A mod for people who like using ElvenWepons and Armor, but hate the low stats, this will change it
descriptionHtml: I noticed that the HeawyElven mod didn\'t fix the Arrows Damage? Well, now it\'s fixed! The mod increases the damage from 16 to 25 damage, not so much actually, but it\'s noticable. If you are like me, a elf, and likes the elven gear, u should use this, because it makes the elven-equipment the best in the game, without overpowering it!
author: SJAPP
